  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Junior Hair Stylist",
  "description": "<p>TONI&GUY Duxton is a boutique, premium hair salon located in the Duxton area. We are looking for a <strong>Junior Hairstylist with hands-on salon experience</strong> who is confident handling clients independently and is looking to grow within a professional, structured environment.</p><p>This role is suitable for stylists who are no longer assisting full-time and are ready to manage their own clients while continuing to refine their technical and consultation skills.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle clients independently for <strong>haircuts, colour services, and treatments</strong></p></li><li><p>Conduct professional consultations and recommend suitable services and aftercare</p></li><li><p>Deliver consistent service quality aligned with salon standards</p></li><li><p>Maintain hygiene, cleanliness, and professional presentation at all times</p></li><li><p>Support overall salon operations and teamwork on the floor</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum 2 years of hands-on salon experience</p></li><li><p>Able to <strong>handle clients independently</strong> for cut, colour, and treatment services for at least past 2 years</p></li><li><p>Hairdressing certification or equivalent training preferred</p></li><li><p>Confident in client consultation and basic service recommendation</p></li><li><p>Having an <strong>existing customer base is an advantage</strong>, but not mandatory</p></li><li><p>Professional attitude, reliability, and willingness to work as part of a team</p></li><li><p>Able to work weekends and retail hours</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li><p>Stable basic salary with commission structure</p></li><li><p>Opportunity to grow client base in a central, established salon</p></li><li><p>Professional working environment with clear service standards</p></li><li><p>Training support and long-term career progression</p></li><li><p>No sales pressure culture — focus on quality work and client retention</p></li></ul>",
